A channel on YouTube called N'kandla Staail have released a satirical video based on rapper Coolio's song Gangster's Paradise. No information was available on the producer of the video, except on the N'kandla Staail Facebook page which says he or she lives in Harare, Zimbabwe.&nbsp;A previous video on the same channel, Nkandla Style, was viewed more than 575 000 times.* The views expressed here are not necessarily those of Independent Media.